Configure AWS IoT core for feedback and print job logs:

1. Create Things

o Navigate to AWS IoT > Manage > Things

o Click on create things

o Create single thing

o Enter thing name > click next

2. Creating Device Certificate

o Click “Auto generate new Certificate” > next

o Click on create Policy

3. Creating Policy and Recourses

o Enter policy name

Policy effect Policy action Policy resource

Allow Publish *

Allow Subscribe *

Allow connect *

Allow Get *

o Create

o Get back to the original tab (where we were creating the thing)

o Select the created policy

o Click “Create thing”

4. Downloading MQTT Policy

o Download the certificates

· Device Certificate

· Public Key

· Private Key

· Root CA1 certificate

· Root CA2 certificate
